This file explains how to install spielterminal from  source code repository.

Prerequisites
=============

- Autotools (autoconf, automake)
- GCC compiler.
- make utility.

Installation
============

Then, you can run 'configure':

  $ ./boostrap
  $ ./configure

Here, you can give as arguments to 'configure'

  - configure options, as listen in the 'configure --help' output.

  $ make
  $ make check
  $ make install
